Acceptance: Code-changing work requires a fresh confirmed plan naming repository, base, scope, runner, and output authority; PR creation accepts only an explicitly supplied branch or that confirmed result and revalidates head/base before dispatch. Cancellation, stale result, duplicate invocation, runner failure, receipt, webhook reconciliation, and disabled rollout gate are tested independently. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-12-github-item-room-routing.md.